stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Scheduled
    Scheduled --> Due: Scheduled time reached
    Due --> Taken: Parent confirms
    Due --> Snoozed: Remind later
    Snoozed --> Due: Snooze expires
    Due --> Skipped: Parent skips
    Due --> Escalated: Need Help
    Due --> Missed: Grace period expires
    Missed --> Escalated: Caregiver notified
    Escalated --> Resolved: Parent/contact/caregiver resolves
    Scheduled --> Cancelled: Schedule changed/stopped
    Due --> Cancelled: Medicine stopped
    Taken --> [*]
    Skipped --> [*]
    Resolved --> [*]
    Cancelled --> [*]

    note right of Taken
      Offline action may enter a queued outbox
      Server sync remains idempotent
    end note
